4, over, knit 2 together,
over, knit 2
together, over, knit
2 together, over, slip 1, knit 1, pull slipped stitch over, knit 1,
over, slip 2, knit 1, pull slipped stitches over, over, knit 2.

11th row       knit 5, over, knit 2 together, over, knit 2 together,
