Knitting pattern (fig. 389).       Cast on a number of stitches
that divides by 9.



Fig. 389. Knitting pattern.

Materials: Cordonnet 6 fils D.M.C, or Fil          pointer D.M.C


1st row       2 overs, slip 1, knit 1, pull slipped stitch over,
